title: Welcome to Deux U by DeuxMoi
description:
If you love the juicy stories you get right here from Sofia, check out Deux U for the juiciest celeb stories of the week.  Deux U is a weekly podcast from the anonymous creator of the pop culture and entertainment news Instagram account @deuxmoi. On every episode, “Deux" - along with insiders and expert guests - shares exclusive details on the hottest celeb stories that haven’t been revealed on Instagram.

Thank you both - let me know if you have any questions!
